    "body": "I can reproduce this issue on CentOS 7 when passing a prefix path to `make install`. This is not a cross compiling build, just a normal build with an install prefix which makes the install calls in the install-headers_cxx too long.\r\n```\r\n$ make --version\r\nGNU Make 4.1\r\nBuilt for x86_64-redhat-linux-gnu\r\n```\r\n```\r\n$ bash --version\r\nGNU bash, version 4.2.46(2)-release (x86_64-redhat-linux-gnu)\r\n```\r\nEdit: still an issue with gRPC 1.13."
